title: keep me - a christian indie folk peaceful playlist
description:
Follow me on Instagram:
https://www.instagram.com/crossgray_/?igshid=NGVhN2U2NjQ0Yg%3D%3D

my name is cross gray and this is a curation of some of my own original songs. I loved the idea of compiling them into an album-like project for my channel, so if you enjoy this style of chill indie christian music, I hope this playlist can be useful for studying, praying, or just relaxing to some folk worship music you may or may not have heard yet.
